Infernal Cauldrons Mini-Game

His Greatness, Lord of Infernal Cauldrons, Infernal Horse hosts this amazing attraction. Put Ether or ETH.TOWN tokens in a cauldron along with other participants, wait, and see who gets the contents. The probability to win depends on how much you put in compared to others. If the pot has 1 ETH and yours is 0.5 ETH, your chance to get everything is 50%, if yours is 0.2 ETH, then 20%. Even 0.001 has a chance to get the whole pot.

ETH.TOWN Roadmap

We want this game to be big and long. We have a lot of ideas and a lot of plans for it. It is designed to be not just a finished product we release at some point, but evolving and expanding. We will be supporting the game, maintaining an active and friendly community and adding more content and mechanics. We will share just the very beginning.

The project roadmap is following:

  • May: Limited access beta (application form at https://eth.town):
  • June: Full launch
  • June: POWH event
  • July: 2 additional mini games
  • July: CryptoKitties event
  • August: CryptoCountries event
